videos.headline: Jordan Hawkins drives and throws it down with authority
videos.description: Jordan Hawkins drives past his defender and rocks the rim to extend the Huskies' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jordan Hawkins drives and throws it down with authority ) 2023/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Curbelo dishes a no-look dime to Soriano for a St. John's bucket
videos.description: Andre Curbelo dishes a sweet no-look dime to Joel Soriano for a Red Storm basket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Curbelo dishes a no-look dime to Soriano for a St. John's bucket) 2023/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: AJ Storr drains the deep 3 from the wing for St. John's
videos.description: AJ Storr lets it fly and knocks down the triple from downtown to regain the lead for the Red Storm.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (AJ Storr drains the deep 3 from the wing for St. John's) 2023/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jordan Hawkins drains back-to-back 3s for UConn
videos.description: Jordan Hawkins gets things started for the Huskies with back-to-back triples to give them a lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jordan Hawkins drains back-to-back 3s for UConn) 2023/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Alex Karaban buries the corner 3 for UConn
videos.description: Alex Karaban pulls up and knocks down the corner 3-pointer to give the Huskies a lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Alex Karaban buries the corner 3 for UConn ) 2023/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dylan Addae-Wusu takes it coast to coast for the bucket
videos.description: Dylan Addae-Wusu gathers the rock and takes it to the hole for an impressive basket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Dylan Addae-Wusu takes it coast to coast for the bucket) 2023/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Calcaterra dimes Karaban for the and-1
videos.description: Alex Karaban gathers the dime from Joey Calcaterra and gets the and-1 to fall to pull the Huskies closer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Calcaterra dimes Karaban for the and-1) 2023/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: AJ Storr hammers it home to extend St. John's lead
videos.description: AJ Storr gathers the rock and slams it home to extend the Red Storm's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (AJ Storr hammers it home to extend St. John's lead) 2023/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Addae-Wusu gets it done on both sides of the ball
videos.description: Dylan Addae-Wusu steals the rock and finishes with the and-1 for the Red Storm.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Addae-Wusu gets it done on both sides of the ball) 2023/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hassan Diarra blows the wide-open slam
videos.description: Hassan Diarra elevates on the fast break and is stuffed by the rim as he misses the wide-open jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hassan Diarra blows the wide-open slam) 2023/01/15 ESHEET
